      <akn:section eId="sec_31_1804">
        <akn:num>31-1804</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Books and records; reinsurance intermediary brokers.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-1804_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>For at least 10 years after expiration of each contract of reinsurance transacted by the reinsurance broker, the reinsurance broker will keep a complete record for each transaction showing:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_31-1804_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>The insurer will have access and the right to copy and audit all accounts and records maintained by the reinsurance broker related to its business in a form usable by the insurer.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
